2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper involves the optimization of power allocation and scheduling, which is a key area of research in information theory. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper involves the development of a computationally efficient online algorithm, which is a key area of research in systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions real-time voice and video, which are applications of multimedia. 
5. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper deals with multihop wireless networks, which involve distributed computing and communication.
